Food Products

Company Overview of Louisiana Sugar Refining LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Louisiana Sugar Refining LLC engages in the refining, production, and distribution of sugar to commercial and retail customers in the United States. The company is based in Gramercy, Louisiana. Louisiana Sugar Refining, LLC operates as a joint venture between Cargill, Incorporated and Sugar Growers and Refiners, Inc.


1230 South 5th AvenueGramercy, LA 70052United StatesFounded in 2010



