Update Profile

Company Profile
Al Khaleej Sugar Company LLC Profile


				
				Al Khaleej Sugar or The Gulf Sugar - appropriately derives its name from the fact that it is the first sugar refinery in the Arabian Gulf Region.The biggest standalone Sugar refinery is located in Jebel Ali in Dubai &has acurrent production capacity of more than 7,000 tons of refined Sugar per day, employing about 800 personnel. In 2011, the refinery set another record in terms of highest ever-annual production of refined sugar at 1.5 million tons. Al Khaleej Sugar procures various grades & Sugar type extracted from Raw Sugar from: Fine & White Sugar, Extra Fine, Coarse Sugar & Sugar Syrup/ Molasses. Sugar are packed in different wholesale & bulk sizes from 50 kg, 1 ton, 1250 KG and 2 tons, distributed to local, Regional & international clients spread in more than 40 countries in the world. - At Al Khaleej Sugar, We are often committed to satisfy your "Sweet" requirements -


