EmploymentLSR
                          is committed to hiring and retaining the area's best available
                          workforce and to ensuring that the refinery operates in the safest,
                          most efficient and environmentally friendly manner.
                        
Initial hiring is conducted in partnership with the Louisiana
                          Workforce Commission through an on-line application and screening
                          process, additional skills assessment, in-person interviews and passage
                          of a physical and drug screening.
                        
Key considerations for employment at LSR include:

 Teamwork orientation 
 Safety orientation 
 Technical competencies 
 Ability to quickly learn new technologies 
 Service professionalism 
 Problem solving 
 Mechanical reasoning 
 Math and reading skills 
 Service professionalism 

